---
title: Creamy Basil Pesto & Pork Fusilli with Garden Salad & Parmesan
description: In this dish, we've teamed rich basil pesto with a silky cream-based sauce, then followed it up with tender pork mince for a meal that looks and smells every bit as good as it tastes.

*Unfortunately, this week's fusilli was in short supply, so some customers will receive farfalle instead. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious, just be sure to follow your recipe card!*
